title: [FSX/P3D] Aerosoft PBY Catalina X v1.20 (New Build)
description:
I managed to find Aerosoft's PBY Catalina X v1.20 somewhere on the internet, but it turned out that v1.20 full installer is buggy as hell and needs some corrections before it works as expected. I fixed the problems as much as I could and built the package into a custom installer for you pirates. Aside from a very small niggle about how the mission is displayed under the mission menu, the package should be bug-free now. The new installer also supports P3D v1 and P3D v2, but remember that this is a fully experimental mod and nothing is guaranteed. Try the package in P3D at your own risk!

In addition to the triple installer for PBY Catalina X, I have also added other goodies such as a new sound set, more bug fixes for P3D v2 and latest version of the Visual C++ Redistributables to the package to get you going at full pace as soon as possible. Read the Readme file included with the upload first for more info; it is probably more than all you will ever need as long as you don't have something wrong in your hardware/software setup. I have a low upload speed, so I can't keep seeding this forever. If you like this package, please seed it for some time.


HUGE THANKS to the original releaser for his generousity!

Seed and enjoy, pirates!
